tid":1134850,"uid":48796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:45:23.000Z","msg":"TVB 心中清楚香港人係奴隸, 外國人係一個完整嘅人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個完整自由嘅人當然可以武力反抗<br />\n但奴隸對主子使一個不滿嘅眼神已經係死罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5ee6822f90959f810513aae51c0d8f7f5b85d7","tid":1134850,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7682cee484a6af09ef31395bf6d8b599a8578f67","tid":1134850,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"941a66b397d9387de82d5e6a47389202b16428f0","tid":1134850,"uid":47020,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"中國香港市大學畢業咪咁"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:03:26.000Z","msg":"中x..浸x.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T09:12:18.000Z","msg":"而家無線近幾年請個D，做本地新聞同主播個堆愈來愈少呢兩間大學新聞系畢業（唔包括其他台過嚟個D），好多都係珠海、城大、樹仁畢業生。"},{"pid":"ce447b87172efff5c30b415c0d83732b4f049c67","tid":1134850,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef3633ced8a4e901f391c1d50585e5a939fc3705","tid":1134850,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:59:28.000Z","msg":"想知班記者logic拎咩grade<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T09:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />旺角衝突特府定性為暴動<br />\n<br />\n好多人都入左暴動罪"},{"pid":"66b5743642878c1addea1865c3cf7f4b7db51448","tid":1134850,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef3633ced8a4e901f391c1d50585e5a939fc3705","tid":1134850,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:59:28.000Z","msg":"想知班記者logic拎咩grade<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T09:24:43.000Z","msg":"唔睇tvb咪得"},{"pid":"7461157b584b5d406af390279a34525c0d401056","tid":1134850,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T09:28:58.000Z","msg":"香港係暴動<br />\n五四係愛國運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ca9ed949ad76f0b5783aa0699c9210feecf2d0","tid":1134850,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T09:29:19.000Z","msg":"過去香港有多次大型示威集會，但2月8日年初一在旺角發生的衝突，是1997年回歸以來，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">特區政府首次定性大型公眾集會為「暴亂」，並引用「暴動罪」起訴部分示威人士。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n在《政府部門常用辭彙》中，並沒有「暴亂」一詞，但觀乎特首梁振英2月9日回應事件時，相對於中文發言使用的「暴亂」，英文發言時使用的是「Riot」，與《政府部門常用辭𢑥》的「暴動」相同。港府定性之後，超過半數傳統傳媒，包括無綫新聞、東方日報、星島日報及經濟日報等，在報導事件時都使用「暴亂」，而成報和親政府網媒「港人港地」，則以「暴動」形容事件。北京官方在2月11 日，也指這是「由個別本土激進分離組織為主策動的暴亂事件」。<br />\n<br />\n原文：《暴亂？衝突？香港媒體怎樣稱呼「旺角騷亂」》 <a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20160217-hongkong-MKPolice-04/?utm_medium=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20160217-hongkong-MKPolice-04%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dcopy&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=28fbd006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20160217-hongkong-MKPolice-04/?utm_medium=copy</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0defb376444ddf64f6eedbe162f2fcb585f64844","tid":1134850,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T09:33:17.000Z","msg":"中國打內戰=解放"}]}